T.rate:
:(t->begin
          policy_days = [20, 60, 120] .+ 17
          contact_rate = 0.05
          pol = findfirst((x->begin
                          t <= x
                      end), policy_days)
          growth_rate = if pol == 1
                  0.0
              else
                  2 ^ (1 / ((pol - 1) * 5)) - 1
              end
          return ((growth_rate + Î³) / 990) * (1 - contact_rate)
      end)
